project.banking

  • Classes in project.banking used by project.banking 
    Class and Description
    BankStatementParser
    Implementation of the interface give an opportunity to user for converting String line to BankTransaction representation.
    BankTransaction
    Class is a data transfer object (DTO).
    BankTransactionFilter
    Interface giving an opportunity to filter ( or test ) BankTransaction according to some condition.
    BankTransactionSummarizer
    The interface is designed to implement the concept of sequential enumeration of all BankTransaction elements in some list.
    Exporter
    Interface giving an opportunity to export SummaryStatistics into different formats (depends on realisation).
    SummaryStatistics
    A domain object representing summary information about the list of transactions, which is exported to file and provided to the user.
